    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract base for type-erased command handler storage. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1CommandHandler" kindref="compound">CommandHandler</ref> is a non-templated base class that enables the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1ResourceRegistry" kindref="compound">ResourceRegistry</ref> to store heterogeneous <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandHandler" kindref="compound">TypedCommandHandler</ref> instances in a uniform collection. It carries no behavior itself; all dispatch logic resides in the derived <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandHandler" kindref="compound">TypedCommandHandler</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandHandler" kindref="compound">TypedCommandHandler</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1ResourceRegistry" kindref="compound">ResourceRegistry</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
